property.name: description
property.value: A small machine made of plastic and metal. As you touch the machine it emits a quiet ting.

property.name: description
property.value: Three short pieces of string tied into a curious knot. You note that each of them is of a different color.

property.name: description
property.value: A plant encased in clear acrylic. By the looks of it, an alien flower.

property.name: description
property.value: A piece of organic material with some characters printed on it. Your equipment is unable to identify the language.

property.name: description
property.value: A delicate device composed of plastic and various rare metals. After scanning the device you conclude that whatever data it might once have contained has long since degraded into meaningless strings of ones and zeros.

property.name: description
property.value: The mummified remains of a lifeform of some kind. Your equipment indicates a high amount of carbon.

property.name: description
property.value: A set of metallic objects of various shapes and sizes. All of the objects seem to be based on six different shapes.

property.name: description
property.value: A soft yellow object made entirely of rubber. Emits a peculiar sound when squeezed.

property.name: description
property.value: Yourself looking back at you through the mirror covering the inner surface of the capsule.

property.name: description
property.value: A glass jar filled with ash. The radioactive materials mixed with the ash match those of the surrounding environment.

property.name: description
property.value: A small titanium cube. It appears to be solid. Each of the sides bears a different engraving.

property.name: description
property.value: Half of a medium sized golden plate. This half seems to contain the numbers "6", "1", "11" and "5".

property.name: description
property.value: Half of a medium sized golden plate. This half seems to contain the numbers "13", "15", "15" and "14".

property.name: description
property.value: A plastic container. A quick scan of the container reveals that contains mostly nitrogen, a smaller part of oxygen and traces of other gases.

property.name: description
property.value: A picture book depicting a star turning into a white dwarf. The pages have spots containing natrium chloride.

property.name: description
property.value: A pair of metal loops. One made of silver and one made of gold. Your equipment detects traces of organic materials.

property.name: description
property.value: A black alumium box with strange markings surrounding it. Inside is a red piece of cloth shaped like a cone.

property.name: description
property.value: An intricate object composed of glass and metal. One side of the object is dominated by what you deduce to be numbers and three metallic pieces of different lenghts pointing at the numbers.

property.name: description
property.value: A metal plate with the symbols "LD34" carved into it. The plate is covered in organic matter and iron oxide.

property.name: description
property.value: A note with the symbols "SO DAMN HUNGRY, BUT MUST DEV GAME LOLOL" drawn on it using various organic materials.

property.name: description
property.value: A large plastic cube made out of comportments of different shapes and sizes. The compartments are filled with sand and decayed organic matter.

property.name: description
property.value: An empty time capsule. Judging by the scenery whoever placed this just wanted to make your job that much harder.

property.name: description
property.value: A living specimen of the "human" species rumored to have ruled over this planet. Apparently this specimen wasn't even aware of all life on its planet being extinguished.
